<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-black dark:text-white p-3 md:p-6 transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Introduction -->
  <div class="p-4 md:p-6 pb-8">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-3">
      <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Gli aggettivi qualificativi aggiungono una qualità al nome e possono essere:
    </p>
    <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 ml-6">
      <p><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <strong>grado positivo</strong> → Il libro è interessante.</p>
      <p><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <strong>comparativo</strong> → più/meno/quanto interessante.</p>
      <p><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <strong>superlativo</strong> → interessantissimo, molto interessante, il più interessante tra…</p>
    </div>
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mt-3 italic ml-6">
      Questo libro è interessante. Anzi, è interessantissimo.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: Identify adjective degrees -->
  <div class="p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
      Sottolinea gli aggettivi qualificativi nelle frasi e indica il loro grado.
    </h2>

    <% adjective_sentences = [
      { text: "Il tuo cane è più affettuoso del mio.", degree: "comparativo di maggioranza" },
      { text: "Mi piace la chitarra: ha un suono molto dolce.", degree: "superlativo assoluto" },
      { text: "Sara ha i capelli lisci come sua sorella.", degree: "comparativo di uguaglianza" },
      { text: "Per il matrimonio di mia zia ho comprato un abito blu.", degree: "positivo" },
      { text: "Il gelato è meno buono di quello che ho mangiato ieri.", degree: "comparativo di minoranza" },
      { text: "Metti la sciarpa, oggi è una giornata freddissima.", degree: "superlativo assoluto" }
    ] %>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <% adjective_sentences.each_with_index do |sentence, index| %>
        <div class="rounded-lg p-3 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><%= sentence[:text] %></span>
          </div>
          <% if index == 0 %>
            <span class="font-semibold text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700 dark:text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-400 text-right"><%= sentence[:degree] %></span>
          <% else %>
            <input type="text"
                   class="w-48 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none focus:border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700"
                   data-fill-blanks-target="input"
                   data-answer="<%= sentence[:degree] %>"
                   data-correct-answer="<%= sentence[:degree] %>"
                   maxlength="40">
          <% end %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2: Superlativo relativo vs assoluto -->
  <div class="p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="true">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
      Clicca sui superlativi relativi<span class="inline-block w-5 h-5 bg-blue-300 rounded ml-1 cursor-pointer" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="blue" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span> e sui superlativi assoluti<span class="inline-block w-5 h-5 bg-violet-300 rounded ml-1 cursor-pointer" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="violet" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span>.
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 leading-relaxed space-y-2 cursor-pointer">
      <p><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Questo è <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="blue" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">il film più divertente</span> che abbia mai visto.</p>
      <p><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Durante la passeggiata nel bosco abbiamo visto degli alberi <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="violet" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">altissimi</span>.</p>
      <p><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> La torta della nonna è <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="violet" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">buonissima</span>.</p>
      <p><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Questo è stato <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="blue" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">il compito più difficile</span> dell'anno.</p>
      <p><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Ho comprato un maglione <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="violet" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">caldissimo</span>.</p>
      <p><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Oggi è stato <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-correct="blue" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight">il giorno meno luminoso</span> della settimana.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 3: Write forms -->
  <div class="p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">3</span>
      Scrivi le forme indicate.
    </h2>

    <% forms = [
      { word: "tenero", form: "comparativo di maggioranza", answer: "più tenero" },
      { word: "allegro", form: "comparativo di minoranza", answer: "meno allegro" },
      { word: "alta", form: "comparativo di uguaglianza", answer: "alta come / tanto alta quanto" },
      { word: "saporita", form: "superlativo relativo", answer: "la più saporita" },
      { word: "leggera", form: "superlativo assoluto", answer: "leggerissima / molto leggera" }
    ] %>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <% forms.each do |item| %>
        <div class="rounded-lg p-3 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
            <span class="font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><%= item[:word] %></span>
            <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">(<%= item[:form] %>)</span>
            <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">→</span>
          </div>
          <input type="text"
                 class="w-48 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none focus:border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700"
                 data-fill-blanks-target="input"
                 data-answer="<%= item[:answer] %>"
                 data-correct-answer="<%= item[:answer] %>"
                 maxlength="40">
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 4: Complete with adjectives -->
  <div class="p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">4</span>
      Completa con aggettivi al grado richiesto.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="rounded-lg p-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Cristian è</span>
        <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none focus:border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="il più alto">
        <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">(superlativo relativo)</span>
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">tra i compagni di basket.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg p-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Ho comprato un</span>
        <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none focus:border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="bellissimo">
        <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">(superlativo assoluto)</span>
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">libro di poesie.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg p-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Le scarpe da ginnastica di Alice sono</span>
        <input type="text" class="w-24 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none focus:border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="rosse">
        <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">(positivo)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg p-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">La campanella della scuola è</span>
        <input type="text" class="w-36 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none focus:border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="rumorosissima">
        <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">(superlativo assoluto)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg p-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Simonetta è</span>
        <input type="text" class="w-28 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none focus:border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="più alta">
        <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">(comparativo di maggioranza)</span>
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">di Paolo.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg p-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span>
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Il Po è</span>
        <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none focus:border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="il più lungo">
        <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">(superlativo relativo)</span>
        <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">dei fiumi d'Italia.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-right text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
    Esercizi pp. <%= link_to "154", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p154"), class: "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-200 underline" %>, <%= link_to "155", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p155"), class: "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-200 underline" %> e <%= link_to "163", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p163"), class: "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-200 underline" %>
  </div>

  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
</div>
